# Styling

- Tailwind CSS 4 with CSS-first configuration. No `tailwind.config.js`.
- Utility-first: compose styles with Tailwind classes in JSX.
- Custom theme values go in `@theme` blocks in `globals.css`.
- Base typography styles are defined in `globals.css` via `@layer base`.
- Avoid inline `style` props unless truly dynamic (e.g., computed values).
- Use arbitrary values `[...]` sparingly; prefer design tokens.
